  "text": "RNA extraction and qRT-PCR. Total RNA was extracted using the method of Reid [CITATION_1] and the primer sets for each gene were designed using Primer Premier 5.0 (Primer, Canada) (Supplementary Table S1 ). qRT-PCR was carried out as Xu et al. [CITATION_2] .",
